{
  "stem": "5516.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I had a couple days and after this, they didn't want nothing to do with me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But I survived, you know.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Let me go back to Germany after the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You stayed-- you said that you were liberated in this town, Bad Hills, is that right?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Is that-- that's where you were liberated?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Where?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 52,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bad Tolz.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they didn't clean out.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Some-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] a German soldier go over, there was a group, maybe five, 10, you know?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There was a lot of them, you know, a lot of soldiers and a lot of groups.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was in a group five, 10 people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We were staying there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 53,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The soldier, an American soldier come over and he say, come with us.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he saw an empty house, an empty house.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When they put us in the house to sleep, in a-- he gave us a bed, I think, it was a bed, I think, for two people.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was in a bed.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "When I was out from bed.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I couldn't sleep in a bed because I'm not accustomed.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I laid down on the floor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I could sleep.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "In the bed, I couldn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "How about-- actually, we're going to change the tape in a second.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Let me just ask you one other question, though.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "With food, were you careful about what you ate right away?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because a lot of times--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This is where you ask till you know something.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You're a good correspondent, you know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] See, a lot of people-- not a lot.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know a lot-- even it's a few.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "See, the American soldiers, they threw out from the jeeps, from their trucks, food, you know, sardines, I don't know what.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
